{"tid":1679730,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"三招安全方法抵抗極權","createTime":"2019-10-28T11:11:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-28T15:59:36.000Z","uid":64810,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1a9e743391150aeafdae2ad6261e4495016d987f","tid":1679730,"uid":64810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T11:11:59.000Z","msg":"1罷買所有野 盡力減低所有經濟活動<br />\n見到咁既時勢 仲邊有心情買野 認証左既黃鋪就除外<br />\n同埋 記得抵制TVB 所有既廣告商 同埋地鐵既廣場及鋪頭<br />\n裝修中資及福建幫鋪頭都十分有效，但裝修時間要快<br />\n<br />\n2.宣傳<br />\n貼文宣係法律風險極低 但狗已經連貼文宣都會拉 所以好需要 星期三/四定立文宣日<br />\n組隊去貼文宣 區近區選 可以貼民賤聯衰野 民賤聯之前幫手通過撥款 幫狗買裝備等<br />\n千奇唔好係路障到貼d起左底既警員資料 會藐視法庭嫁 人地清路障個陣會難堪嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3.罷交稅<br />\n所有既稅項 都用幾蚊碎銀既方法交<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n死左/被捕既手足一定唔想我地就咁放棄 呢場運動我地一定要走落去！唔好氣餒 堅持五大訴求<br />\n我都希望有朝一日 香港能夠一個星期罷工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e3a52b6480d25468806d37fdd11aa061ff55cc1","tid":1679730,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T11:12:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qXEs9qi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqXEs9qi.jpg&h=02cd3311&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"ee22fc8212ee8d2c75e115a4b5f015a2a52d9e91","tid":1679730,"uid":64810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T11:18:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae0bb464fd868d39688e084e8f12acbe7a3051eb","tid":1679730,"uid":64810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T11:20:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c85fa4cb8e35f31c488c7632c17e99